sources.description: THE RAGTIME BAND  Keystone-Mutual 1 reel, rel. May 1, 1913 (the Band) also the Jazz Band  Dir. Mack Sennett cast: Mabel Normand, Ford Sterling, Alice Davenport,  Nick Cogley finished 3/27/1913 (With sound.) Note. Compare this film with "Max Plays at Drama" with Max Linder -- also on the Internet Archive. William Thomas Sherman, wts@gunjones.com, http://www.angelfire.com/mn/hp/
